TICKET APP - Anderson Armani

API - http://developer.ticketmaster.com/products-and-docs/apis/discovery-api/v2/

Libraries:
	//Gson
	Parser Json used in webserver requests

    //Retrofit
    HTTP WebServer

    //RxJava2
    Reactive programm 

    //Picasso
    Image loader

    //Room
    Users favorites' Database


IMPLEMENTATION:
	Tickets Activity - load some tickets from API TicketMaster and show each one as a Card;
		Card click Action - ADD / Remove item from Favorite list (Room Database)
		Item Menu - Intent for the Favorites Activity

	Favorites Activity - List the user favorites in Descendent order
		Item Swipe (Left or Right) remove item from Database

IMPROVEMENTS:
	Implement MVVM
	Separate context
	Create a data repository for cache data and persist data locally
	Request pagination using RxJava
	Use different design
	Implement filter on Events Activity
	ADD Event Detail Activity
	Implement share event functiunality
	...

